title: Senate Races to Watch on Election Night
description: Republicans are hopeful they can capture control of the Senate, but Democrats are taking aim at some wobbly G.O.P. candidates who are very loyal to Trump.
dc:creator: Jonathan Weisman

media:content.media:credit: John Tully for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Don Bolduc, the Republican Senate candidate in New Hampshire, is in a tight race against the incumbent, Senator Maggie Hassan.
